abstract: Data reflecting less than improvement in housing and dented consumer confidence caused investors to curb their recent enthusiasm.
snippet: Data reflecting less than improvement in housing and dented consumer confidence caused investors to curb their recent enthusiasm.
lead_paragraph: Faced with new figures showing a decline in consumer confidence, investors struggled to find some of their own on Tuesday.

headline.main: Wall St. Ends a Cautious Day Mixed
headline.print_headline: Wall St. Ends a Cautious Day Mixed
